s=\"footnote\">13. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116943\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116943)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116943)\">Moses 7:69<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">14. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112175\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 112175)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(112175)\">Alma 34:39<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">15. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106304\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106304)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106304)\">Deut. 13:4<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"115005\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 115005)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(115005)\">D&amp;C 93:1<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">16. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111923\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111923)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111923)\">Alma 12:37<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111927\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111927)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111927)\">Alma 13:6<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114656\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114656)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114656)\">D&amp;C 84:24<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">17. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"117176\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 117176)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(117176)\">JS&mdash;H 1 Endnote<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">18. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114071\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114071)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114071)